      "relations": null,
      "text": [
        " قَالَ رَسُولُ اللَّهِ ( صلى الله عليه وآله ) مُجَالَسَةُ أَهْلِ الدِّينِ شَرَفُ الدُّنْيَا وَ الْآخِرَةِ ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "Muhammad Bin Ismail, from Al Fazl Bin Shazan, from Ibn Abu Umeyr, from Mansour bin Hazim, ",
          "(It has been narrated) from Abu Abdullah<sup>asws</sup> having said: ‘Rasool-Allah<sup>saww</sup> said: ‘The gatherings of the people of the Religion is a nobility in the world and the Hereafter’’."
        ],
        "en.sarwar": [
          " 4. Muhammad ibn ‘Ism’il has narrated from al-Fadl ibn Shadha from ibn abu ‘Umayr from Mansur ibn Hazim from abu ‘Abdallah (a.s.) who has said the following. “The holy Prophet said, ‘Association with religious people is a honor in this life as well as in the next life.’”"
        ]
      }
